{"tid":1509000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"頭條日報:警方以機場有禁制令為由　禁止職工盟周三國泰城集會","createTime":"2019-08-26T16:38:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T00:11:44.000Z","uid":118922,"like":3,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"38f178c0d3e0dd02a67907cfe6d11e217f8bdbfe","tid":1509000,"uid":118922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T16:38:51.000Z","msg":"持續兩個多月的反修例風波中，國泰航空備受壓力，解僱多名員工，就連港龍工會主席施安娜亦疑因社交平台個人言論而被解僱，職工盟發起周三（28日）在國泰城集會。不過職工盟秘書長李卓人在facebook表示，警方以機場有禁制令為理由，禁止國泰城集會 。<br />\n<br />\n職工盟強烈遣責警方剝奪市民集會自由，並即時申請向公眾集會和遊行上訴委員會上訴。<br />\n<br />\n職工盟原擬今日(周一)在國泰城舉行集會，不滿公司在反對修訂《逃犯條例》風波下，解僱多名航空界從業員，但由於未取得警方的「不反對通知書」，將集會推遲至周三舉行，以便有足夠時間申請「不反對通知書」，但終被警方反對。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d1b2c8d72dd056993f9d31d9c16dc9241305711","tid":1509000,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T16:39:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrnaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=f4f43136\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrnaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=9df4649a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrnaXPXn3VG1rM